name: Cheesy Party Cottage Pies Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Line a baking tray with baking paper.
Heat pies and potato minis in a microwave for 3 minutes or until slightly defrosted. Peel pastry lids off the pies.

Top each pie with cheese and potato minis, pressing down slightly, and place on prepared tray. Bake pies for 20 minutes or until potato minis are golden and pies are heated through. Serve with tomato sauce.
